short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Generate a Google Profile review link quickly, without needing access to the account.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Generate a Google Profile review link quickly, without needing access to the account.

Simply add the extension to your browser, Google Search the business and find their Google Profile page and then click the extension icon. That's it! You now have the Google review link for the business.
